Global Screw Type Mortar Spraying Machine Market Insights
Screw Type Mortar Spraying Machine Market size was valued at USD 1.5 Billion in 2022 and is projected to reach USD 2.8 Billion by 2030, growing at a CAGR of 8.5% from 2024 to 2030.

Screw Type Mortar Spraying Machine Market Overview
The global screw type mortar spraying machine market has witnessed substantial growth in recent years, valued at USD 3.2 billion in 2024. The demand for these machines is anticipated to reach USD 5.1 billion by 2032, growing at a compound annual growth rate (CAGR) of 6.3% from 2025 to 2032. This market expansion is driven by the growing construction and infrastructure development activities globally, as well as technological advancements that improve the efficiency and durability of these machines. The increasing adoption of automated machinery for precise and rapid application of mortar also fuels market growth. Factors such as labor shortages and the need for faster construction timelines contribute significantly to the demand for screw type mortar spraying machines across various regions.

